parameters.query:
INSERT INTO garmin_daily_stats (
  date,
  sleep_score,
  sleep_duration_minutes,
  deep_sleep_minutes,
  light_sleep_minutes,
  rem_sleep_minutes,
  awake_minutes,
  body_battery_start,
  body_battery_end,
  body_battery_charged,
  body_battery_drained,
  stress_avg,
  stress_max,
  rest_stress_minutes,
  low_stress_minutes,
  medium_stress_minutes,
  high_stress_minutes,
  steps,
  active_calories,
  total_calories,
  intensity_minutes,
  floors_climbed,
  resting_hr,
  hrv_status,
  hrv_value,
  synced_at
) VALUES (
  '{{ $json.date }}',
  {{ $json.sleep_score || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.sleep_duration_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.deep_sleep_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.light_sleep_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.rem_sleep_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.awake_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.body_battery_start || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.body_battery_end || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.body_battery_charged || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.body_battery_drained || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.stress_avg || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.stress_max || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.rest_stress_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.low_stress_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.medium_stress_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.high_stress_minutes || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.steps || 0 }},
  {{ $json.active_calories || 0 }},
  {{ $json.total_calories || 0 }},
  {{ $json.intensity_minutes || 0 }},
  {{ $json.floors_climbed || 0 }},
  {{ $json.resting_hr || 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.hrv_status ? "'" + $json.hrv_status + "'" : 'NULL' }},
  {{ $json.hrv_value || 'NULL' }},
  NOW()
)
ON CONFLICT (date) DO UPDATE SET
  sleep_score = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.sleep_score, garmin_daily_stats.sleep_score),
  sleep_duration_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.sleep_duration_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.sleep_duration_minutes),
  deep_sleep_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.deep_sleep_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.deep_sleep_minutes),
  light_sleep_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.light_sleep_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.light_sleep_minutes),
  rem_sleep_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.rem_sleep_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.rem_sleep_minutes),
  awake_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.awake_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.awake_minutes),
  body_battery_start = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.body_battery_start, garmin_daily_stats.body_battery_start),
  body_battery_end = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.body_battery_end, garmin_daily_stats.body_battery_end),
  body_battery_charged = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.body_battery_charged, garmin_daily_stats.body_battery_charged),
  body_battery_drained = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.body_battery_drained, garmin_daily_stats.body_battery_drained),
  stress_avg = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.stress_avg, garmin_daily_stats.stress_avg),
  stress_max = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.stress_max, garmin_daily_stats.stress_max),
  rest_stress_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.rest_stress_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.rest_stress_minutes),
  low_stress_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.low_stress_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.low_stress_minutes),
  medium_stress_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.medium_stress_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.medium_stress_minutes),
  high_stress_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.high_stress_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.high_stress_minutes),
  steps = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.steps, garmin_daily_stats.steps),
  active_calories = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.active_calories, garmin_daily_stats.active_calories),
  total_calories = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.total_calories, garmin_daily_stats.total_calories),
  intensity_minutes = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.intensity_minutes, garmin_daily_stats.intensity_minutes),
  floors_climbed = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.floors_climbed, garmin_daily_stats.floors_climbed),
  resting_hr = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.resting_hr, garmin_daily_stats.resting_hr),
  hrv_status = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.hrv_status, garmin_daily_stats.hrv_status),
  hrv_value = COALESCE(EXCLUDED.hrv_value, garmin_daily_stats.hrv_value),
  synced_at = NOW()
RETURNING *

INSERT INTO sync_status (id, source, entity_type, last_sync_at, status, records_synced)
VALUES (gen_random_uuid(), 'garmin', 'daily_stats', NOW(), 'success', 1)
ON CONFLICT (source, entity_type) DO UPDATE SET
  last_sync_at = NOW(),
  status = 'success',
  records_synced = 1,
  error_message = NULL

parameters.text:
=:warning: **Schlechter Schlaf Alert!**

Dein Sleep Score heute: **{{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.sleep_score }}/100**

:crescent_moon: Schlafdauer: {{ Math.floor($('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.sleep_duration_minutes / 60) }}h {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.sleep_duration_minutes % 60 }}min
:purple_circle: Tiefschlaf: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.deep_sleep_minutes || 0 }} min
:blue_circle: Leichtschlaf: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.light_sleep_minutes || 0 }} min
:large_blue_circle: REM: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.rem_sleep_minutes || 0 }} min
:red_circle: Wach: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.awake_minutes || 0 }} min

**Empfehlungen:**
- Heute leichtes Training oder Ruhetag
- Frueher ins Bett gehen
- Koffein vor 14 Uhr vermeiden
- Abends auf Bildschirme verzichten

=:white_check_mark: **Garmin Sync Complete**

:sleeping: Sleep: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.sleep_score || 'N/A' }}/100
:battery: Body Battery: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.body_battery_start || 'N/A' }}%
:chart_with_downwards_trend: Stress: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.stress_avg || 'N/A' }}
:footprints: Steps: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.steps?.toLocaleString() || '0' }}
:heart: Resting HR: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.resting_hr || 'N/A' }} bpm
:heartpulse: HRV: {{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.hrv_value || 'N/A' }} ms ({{ $('Upsert Garmin Data').item.json.hrv_status || 'N/A' }})
